data.description: RECENT PRICE REDUCTION! Come check out this gorgeous home! Don't wait for new construction! This Impression Home Hampton floorplan is ready to move in! Built in 2021 and barely lived in. 5th bedroom optioned in for study and extended covered patio to enjoy for entertainment!  Wood-look tile throughout main living areas. Beautiful open-concept home has 5 bedrooms, 3 baths and 2 car garage. Spacious master bedroom with ensuite master bath with large walk in closet, dual vanity sinks, garden tub and separate shower.  Beautiful kitchen over looking family room with built-in stainless steel appliances. Large pantry and kitchen island. Solar panels installed in May 2022. Tall ceilings throughout home. You don't want to miss out on this beautiful home. Seller offering $2500 towards closing cost. Please include in offer
